---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="EU DORA operational resilience readiness for financial sector organizations. Build ICT risk management and prepare for supervisory oversight.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="EU DORA Readiness for Financial Sector Organizations"
    subheadline="Build operational resilience. Meet EU requirements for ICT risk management. Prepare for supervisory oversight."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why DORA Compliance Matters</h2>
    <p>The Digital Operational Resilience Act creates comprehensive ICT risk management requirements for the EU financial sector. Without a structured approach, organizations face enforcement action, supervisory scrutiny, and operational vulnerability.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Meet EU Regulatory Requirements</h3>
        <p>DORA applies to virtually all EU financial entities and their critical ICT providers, creating enforceable requirements for ICT risk management, incident reporting, and resilience testing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Build Operational Resilience</h3>
        <p>DORA requires comprehensive ICT risk management and operational resilience testing, ensuring financial entities can withstand, respond to, and recover from ICT disruptions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Manage ICT Third-Party Risk</h3>
        <p>Critical ICT third-party providers face direct EU supervisory oversight under DORA, with requirements for concentration risk management and exit strategies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Prepare for Incident Reporting</h3>
        <p>DORA mandates harmonized ICT incident classification and reporting to competent authorities, requiring established processes and templates before incidents occur.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your DORA compliance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Resilience Program</h3>
        <p>Build ICT risk management and testing</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Third-Party ICT</h3>
        <p>Manage provider risk and concentration</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Ongoing Compliance</h3>
        <p>Maintain DORA readiness year-round</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're preparing for DORA compliance for the first time or need help strengthening your operational resilience program, we can help you meet EU requirements with confidence.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
